ence_n_6392036.html | title=House Majority Whip Steve Scalise Spoke At White Supremacist Conference In 2002 | work=The Huffington Post | date=December 29, 2014 | accessdate=December 29, 2014 | author=Reilly, Mollie and Grim, Ryan | archive-date=2014-12-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229215627/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/29/steve-scalise-euro-conference_n_6392036.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://cenlamar.com/2014/12/28/house-majority-whip-steve-scalise-was-reportedly-an-honored-guest-at-2002-international-white-supremacist-convention/|title=House Majority Whip Steve Scalise Was Reportedly an Honored Guest at 2002 International White Supremacist Convention|publisher=|accessdate=29 December 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229214722/http://cenlamar.com/2014/12/28/house-majority-whip-steve-scalise-was-reportedly-an-honored-guest-at-2002-international-white-supremacist-convention/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Calderone>{{cite web | url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/30/lamar-white-jr-scalise-blogger_n_6397078.html | title=How Louisiana Blogger Lamar White, Jr. Landed The Steve Scalise White Supremacist Scoop | work=[[Huffington_Post|Huffington Post]] | date=December 30, 2014 | accessdate=December 31, 2014 | author=Calderone, Michael | archive-date=2014-12-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231114315/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/30/lamar-white-jr-scalise-blogger_n_6397078.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。新闻爆发后，斯卡利斯迅速将公正道歉，并解释在当时，他并知道这个团体的“种族主义本质”<ref name=Martin>{{cite web | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/31/us/politics/scalises-speech-to-white-supremacist-group-clouds-republicans-plans.html | title=Republicans Try to Fix Damage Scalise’s 2002 Speech Could Do in 2016 | work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] | date=December 31, 2014 | accessdate=December 31, 2014 | author=Martin, jonathan and Calmes, Jackie | archive-date=2015-06-02 | archive-url=https:/